	access point or existing infrastructure. We present Ad-hoc On Demand
	Distance Vector Routing (AODV), a novel algorithm for the operation
	of such ad-hoc networks. Each mobile host operates as a specialized
	router, and routes are obtained as needed (i.e., on-demand) with
	little or no reliance on periodic advertisements. Our new routing
